			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Rowania Posted about not getting +1 to all stats until hitting 78 wins.
<br />
This is an answer to that.
<br />

<br />

<br />
It is every 50 wins that you get +1 to all stats. It CAN take you 78 TOTAL wins, but that means youve only upgraded your charm 5 TimES, not 7 times!
<br />

<br />
Example :
<br />
Ruj - 22     - 2 upgrades
<br />
Tak - 19    - 1 upgrade
<br />
Guk - 8     - 0 upgrades
<br />
Mir - 10     - 1 upgrade
<br />
Mist - 19    - 1 upgrade
<br />

<br />
Total - 78   - 5 upgrades!
<br />

<br />
You get one upgrade for every 10 wins. You got 5 upgrades with my example and that is = to 50 Wins!
<br />

<br />
Hope this helped some of you understand better.</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"></td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote"></td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
