<br />

<br />
I have 30 wins in tak also. I didn't pay attention, but i think it went:
<br />
Ruanya Windleaf wins 1-10, at 12 she sent me to Farwein Windrun, an he sent me back to her at win 22. 
<br />

<br />
I don't get a story from them when they send me to the next person, but the person they send me to will give me a story. (Takes 5 storys to get +2hp/mana, and at +10hp/mana you get +1 to all stats. If your below level 65 you don't get +1 to all stats untill your stone hits +10 hp/mana or goes above it. My stone was +11 hp/mana befor i got +1 to all stats due to me being 62)
<br />

<br />
Aslo it seems no one likes to talk to you untill you get sent to them. I tried to skip Hailing Ruanya with one character cuase I knew she was gona just send me to Farwien. I went to so ro  an Farwien just gave me generic text till I went back to Ruanya. &lt;- Ofcorse this could have also been a mistake made by me, either case I just hail them till they send me else where now.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1051878" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: green">Zelousi Dammifudo</span></a><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Mage</a> 
