				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Just a note on Charm augment progresion. At Miraguls you gain the following:
<br />

<br />
10 wins +2 hp/mana
<br />
20 wins +2 hp/mana (+4 total)
<br />
30 wins +2 hp/mana (+6 total)
<br />
40 wins +3 hp/mana (+9 total)
<br />
50 wins +3 hp/mana (+12 total)
<br />
60 wins +3 hp/mana (+15 total)
<br />

<br />
Haven't hit 70 wins yet or the end of the stories, I'm guessing at +20 hp/mana the Miraguls portion of the charm will be maxed.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1051878" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: green">Zelousi Dammifudo</span></a><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Mage</a> 
